Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶们  在破坏世界前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把那只苍蝇收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏…世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏…保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇哉的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？还在等什么  快点杀了它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇哉…要被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:02:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是Nastroyka现象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇哉·布里吉斯才是最棒的触媒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity1  听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在通信圈内就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光线级已经消灭了
