Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗  Argos1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正赶往你们那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没事吗
